MatchHandler - Class in it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.server.controller
The is The Controller of the entire Gameplay, the server is the only one that makes decision about the match, this class has the references to every model object and uses the methods of it, it also decides the commands to send to the clients and handles the commands arrived by every client, an instance of MatchHandler exist for every Match created by the server

Instantiates a new match handler.
MatchHandlerObserver - Interface in it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.server.controller
This interface is used to implement the MVC pattern between the two ClientHandler concrete classes and the MatchHandler.
MatchObserver - Interface in it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.server.observers
This interface is implemented by the MatchHandler class.
